title: Jai Parkash Dalal
text: Jai Parkash Dalal is an Indian politician. He was elected to the <a href="Haryana%20Legislative%20Assembly">Haryana Legislative Assembly</a> from <a href="Loharu%20%28Vidhan%20Sabha%20constituency%29">Loharu</a> in the <a href="2019%20Haryana%20Legislative%20Assembly%20election">2019 Haryana Legislative Assembly election</a> as a member of the <a href="Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party">Bharatiya Janata Party</a>.
